            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A done-for-you SEO service handles strategy, execution, and reporting for you — typically including keyword research, content creation, on-page optimisation, link building, and monthly reporting. Pricing ranges from $49/mo (productised) to $5,000+/mo (full-service).</p></div></div>
